1
00:00:00,560 --> 00:00:02,320
Is that so?

2
00:00:02,320 --> 00:00:04,480
Then, would you like to hold my hand?

3
00:00:04,480 --> 00:00:07,000
♫ <i> Approaching is prohibited </i> ♫

4
00:00:07,000 --> 00:00:08,390
What?

5
00:00:14,140 --> 00:00:17,820
<i> [The Witch Store]</i>

6
00:00:17,820 --> 00:00:23,040
<i> [Episode 8] 
 [What Happens on Double Dates]</i>

7
00:00:23,040 --> 00:00:24,840
Eunah, what do I do?

8
00:00:24,840 --> 00:00:26,856
Why do you think Yuho asked me out?

9
00:00:26,856 --> 00:00:29,340
Why do you think? He obviously asked you out on a date.

10
00:00:29,340 --> 00:00:30,780
I am certain.

11
00:00:30,780 --> 00:00:33,860
Last time you said you were certain that he's into me too.

12
00:00:33,860 --> 00:00:38,880
That's not true. I was only 92,7% sure then.

13
00:00:38,880 --> 00:00:40,560
Come on.

14
00:00:40,560 --> 00:00:42,340
Seriously, what should we do tomorrow?

15
00:00:42,340 --> 00:00:44,096
What do you and Taeil do when you guys hang out together?

16
00:00:44,096 --> 00:00:47,780
Me? I don't really hang out with Taeil these days.

17
00:00:47,780 --> 00:00:50,520
You should have used that healing item with me!

18
00:00:50,520 --> 00:00:52,820
Stay quiet!

19
00:00:52,820 --> 00:00:54,880
I see that you guys are hanging out again.

20
00:00:56,340 --> 00:00:59,220
By the way, aren't you working tomorrow?

21
00:00:59,220 --> 00:01:01,559
Oh, you're right! I've got my part-time job!

22
00:01:01,560 --> 00:01:04,680
Wow. Did you forget about it?

23
00:01:04,680 --> 00:01:06,860
<i>Message!</i>

24
00:01:06,860 --> 00:01:08,119
<i>The store will be closed tomorrow.</i>

25
00:01:08,120 --> 00:01:12,240
I just got a text that the store will be closed tomorrow.

26
00:01:12,240 --> 00:01:16,120
Oh, wow. Maybe she figured out that you have a date tomorrow, and she's trying to help.

27
00:01:16,120 --> 00:01:20,316
Nope. That would never happen.

28
00:01:20,316 --> 00:01:21,660
Okay...

29
00:01:24,020 --> 00:01:26,036
Hey! Seriously! Do you have a death wish?

30
00:01:26,036 --> 00:01:28,260
You just got me killed!

31
00:01:30,000 --> 00:01:32,440
<i> What should I write?</i>

32
00:01:32,440 --> 00:01:35,060
<i> "Youngji, what are you up to tomorrow?"</i>

33
00:01:35,060 --> 00:01:36,980
<i> Hmm... Is that too random?</i>

34
00:01:37,580 --> 00:01:41,440
<i> "Youngji! I found this really nice cake place.</i>

35
00:01:41,440 --> 00:01:43,660
<i> Do you want to go check it out tomorrow?"</i>

36
00:01:43,660 --> 00:01:46,540
<i> Should we go together...</i>

37
00:01:46,540 --> 00:01:48,880
<i> Together...</i>

38
00:01:48,880 --> 00:01:50,616
Hey, what are you up to? Let's go.

39
00:01:50,616 --> 00:01:51,976
<i> Let's go check it out together.</i>

40
00:01:51,976 --> 00:01:53,680
Oh, crap!

41
00:01:54,900 --> 00:01:56,960
I just sent it to her because of you!

42
00:01:57,820 --> 00:01:59,316
What the...

43
00:01:59,316 --> 00:02:01,100
I'm heading out first.

44
00:02:02,740 --> 00:02:04,280
<i> Youngji! I found this really nice cake place. Let's go check it out together.</i>

45
00:02:05,880 --> 00:02:07,520
<i>Okay.</i>

46
00:02:23,640 --> 00:02:26,560
This was the best cake I've ever tasted.

47
00:02:26,560 --> 00:02:29,400
That's nice. Apparently, this is a really famous place.

48
00:02:29,400 --> 00:02:30,880
Is it?

49
00:02:30,880 --> 00:02:33,100
Have you ever been here?

50
00:02:33,100 --> 00:02:34,760
No. This is my first time too.

51
00:02:34,760 --> 00:02:37,956
I've never been here, and I've never tasted a cake before in my life.

52
00:02:37,956 --> 00:02:40,200
I guess this is what a cake tastes like.

53
00:02:40,760 --> 00:02:42,560
It's... It's good.

54
00:02:43,400 --> 00:02:46,980
<i> Why are we taking a dessert tour all of a sudden?</i>

55
00:02:46,980 --> 00:02:50,320
<i> What do you think? Cakes or macarons? Which tastes better?</i>

56
00:02:50,320 --> 00:02:52,680
<i> I don't know. They all taste the same.</i>

57
00:02:52,680 --> 00:02:55,980
<i> Hurry, finish up. We got to check out the waffle place too.</i>

58
00:03:02,240 --> 00:03:03,740
<i> Try this roll cake too.</i>

59
00:03:05,420 --> 00:03:07,040
<i> Why aren't you eating though?</i>

60
00:03:07,040 --> 00:03:10,240
<i> - I don't like cakes. 
 - I don't like you.</i>

61
00:03:12,140 --> 00:03:13,800
Should we order those two too?

62
00:03:13,800 --> 00:03:15,919
Then, we would be trying everything on the menu here.

63
00:03:15,920 --> 00:03:17,816
All right! Let's get them too.

64
00:03:17,816 --> 00:03:19,860
Don't you think it's a little too much, though?

65
00:03:19,860 --> 00:03:21,340
Are you underestimating me?

66
00:03:21,340 --> 00:03:24,560
No, I am not...

67
00:03:25,220 --> 00:03:27,900
It looks delicious. Let's dig in.

68
00:03:28,560 --> 00:03:29,980
It's on me.

69
00:03:29,980 --> 00:03:34,020
No! I brought you here. It's on me.

70
00:03:34,020 --> 00:03:38,240
Excuse me! Can we get one chocolate cake and one strawberry cake please?

71
00:03:38,240 --> 00:03:40,820
Oh wait. Can we get two of each?

72
00:03:42,020 --> 00:03:43,400
What?

73
00:03:50,960 --> 00:03:52,020
You guys!

74
00:03:52,020 --> 00:03:54,076
- You go first. 
 - No, you go first.

75
00:03:54,076 --> 00:03:55,780
Well...

76
00:03:55,780 --> 00:03:58,320
Didn't you say you and Hyeji have some place to go?

77
00:03:58,320 --> 00:03:59,519
Oh, right. I did!

78
00:03:59,520 --> 00:04:01,360
Didn't you say you had to go somewhere too?

79
00:04:01,360 --> 00:04:03,500
Oh yes, I did!

80
00:04:03,500 --> 00:04:05,976
- Well, it's a bummer. 
 - It would've been nice if we could hang out together.

81
00:04:05,976 --> 00:04:07,080
I know, right.

82
00:04:07,080 --> 00:04:09,260
- It's so unfortunate that we've got other things to do today. 
 - Exactly.

83
00:04:09,260 --> 00:04:11,040
- I will see you at school then. 
 - All right.

84
00:04:11,040 --> 00:04:12,960
Thanks... No, I mean. Bye!

85
00:04:12,960 --> 00:04:14,680
- Yep. Bye! 
 - Yep, see you!

86
00:04:14,680 --> 00:04:16,380
Let's go!

87
00:04:16,380 --> 00:04:18,076
Where are we headed now?

88
00:04:18,076 --> 00:04:19,840
Let's go.

89
00:04:33,820 --> 00:04:35,599
How are you are so good at this?!

90
00:04:35,600 --> 00:04:36,960
How are you hanging in there?

91
00:04:36,960 --> 00:04:38,940
It's harder than I expected.

92
00:04:38,940 --> 00:04:40,780
I think I might fall.

93
00:04:40,780 --> 00:04:42,560
Yeah?

94
00:04:42,560 --> 00:04:45,460
Then, would you like to hold my hand?

95
00:04:47,340 --> 00:04:48,680
What?

96
00:05:01,120 --> 00:05:04,420
Just loosen up and straighten your back.

97
00:05:04,420 --> 00:05:07,460
- Whoa! 
 - How is it? Better, right?

98
00:05:07,460 --> 00:05:09,120
Now, slowly let go of my hand.

99
00:05:09,120 --> 00:05:11,980
No! Don't let go!

100
00:05:11,980 --> 00:05:14,140
See? You are good.

101
00:05:14,140 --> 00:05:16,520
I think I might be a little talented. Oops!

102
00:05:16,520 --> 00:05:17,740
I am so sorry!

103
00:05:17,740 --> 00:05:21,040
Hey, watch it!

104
00:05:22,220 --> 00:05:23,600
- What? 
 - What?

105
00:05:25,760 --> 00:05:27,720
- Hyeji, are you okay? 
 - Youngji, are you okay?

106
00:05:29,220 --> 00:05:30,740
- What? 
 - What?

107
00:05:33,130 --> 00:05:39,000
♫ <i> Yeah. Swag. Rock, paper, scissors </i> ♫

108
00:05:39,000 --> 00:05:40,900
What a coincidence.

109
00:05:40,900 --> 00:05:43,536
That's what I am saying. How did you guys end up here?

110
00:05:43,536 --> 00:05:46,940
I followed him here since he told me this place has some amazing corndogs.

111
00:05:46,940 --> 00:05:49,140
I've never been here actually.

112
00:05:51,160 --> 00:05:53,140
Yuho? How about you?

113
00:05:53,140 --> 00:05:54,960
It's my first time here too.

114
00:05:55,440 --> 00:05:57,920
<i> - It's certain. 
 - It's certain.</i>

115
00:05:57,920 --> 00:05:59,920
<i> He checked out the same blog.</i>

116
00:06:02,180 --> 00:06:04,360
The corndog here is amazing.

117
00:06:04,360 --> 00:06:07,520
Yeah? Do you want mine too?

118
00:06:07,520 --> 00:06:09,320
Thank you.

119
00:06:09,320 --> 00:06:11,340
Hyeji, you take mine too.

120
00:06:11,340 --> 00:06:13,660
I am fine though.

121
00:06:13,660 --> 00:06:15,280
<i> Thanks...</i>

122
00:06:16,060 --> 00:06:18,240
By the way,

123
00:06:19,020 --> 00:06:21,040
are you two like,

124
00:06:22,580 --> 00:06:23,776
dating?

125
00:06:23,776 --> 00:06:25,440
- What? 
 - What?

126
00:06:26,460 --> 00:06:29,000
I mean, it's the weekend and you guys are hanging out together.

127
00:06:29,000 --> 00:06:30,720
How about you guys then?

128
00:06:30,720 --> 00:06:33,099
I am here just because he offered good food.

129
00:06:33,100 --> 00:06:34,350
What?

130
00:06:35,080 --> 00:06:37,700
Yeah. That's right.

131
00:06:38,320 --> 00:06:40,300
I asked her to see me today.

132
00:06:41,500 --> 00:06:45,880
The cake we had before... It wasn't so bad.

133
00:06:45,880 --> 00:06:47,860
Other than the fact that the portion was a little small.

134
00:06:47,860 --> 00:06:49,599
I know so many other nice places.

135
00:06:49,600 --> 00:06:50,999
We can go check them out later.

136
00:06:51,000 --> 00:06:54,940
What a good boy, you are!

137
00:06:54,940 --> 00:06:59,280
In that sense, should we grab another cup noodle?

138
00:07:00,080 --> 00:07:01,820
I'll go buy it.

139
00:07:01,820 --> 00:07:05,140
I will join you. I will go get something to drink.

140
00:07:09,360 --> 00:07:12,340
<i> Why is she so tactless?!</i>

141
00:07:18,400 --> 00:07:20,640
Don't even think of stealing my corndog.

142
00:07:23,660 --> 00:07:26,340
<i> Sungwoo, I feel you. Cheer up.</i>

143
00:07:37,440 --> 00:07:40,080
<i> [Yuho]</i>

144
00:07:41,120 --> 00:07:43,340
Hey, Yuho, are you home?

145
00:07:43,340 --> 00:07:45,579
Hyeji, you left your purse!

146
00:07:45,580 --> 00:07:46,880
Oh, really?

147
00:07:46,880 --> 00:07:48,700
Do you think you can step outside for a moment?

148
00:07:48,700 --> 00:07:51,320
Yes! I will be right there!

149
00:08:02,380 --> 00:08:03,940
Yuho!

150
00:08:03,940 --> 00:08:05,440
Here you go.

151
00:08:05,440 --> 00:08:08,880
Thank you. You could've just held on to it until we saw each other at school on Monday.

152
00:08:10,840 --> 00:08:13,560
- Well, Hyeji. 
 - Yeah?

153
00:08:16,960 --> 00:08:18,360
I...

154
00:08:20,740 --> 00:08:22,240
I...

155
00:08:24,420 --> 00:08:26,140
I like you.

156
00:08:28,860 --> 00:08:31,320
<i> What are the chances?</i>

157
00:08:31,320 --> 00:08:34,680
<i> What are the chances of your crush having a crush on you?</i>

158
00:08:35,330 --> 00:08:44,200
♫ <i> Shine on me like those stars. Close your eyes and 
 remember me. That magic when it started</i> ♫

159
00:08:44,200 --> 00:08:47,860
<i> Youngji would... Tteokbokki?</i>

160
00:08:49,140 --> 00:08:50,456
<i> No, hamburger...</i>

161
00:08:50,456 --> 00:08:53,160
<i> - Hey, Sungwoo. 
 - Yeah?</i>

162
00:08:53,160 --> 00:08:56,160
<i> - You like Youngji, right? 
 - Yeah.</i>

163
00:08:57,940 --> 00:08:59,800
<i> How did you know?</i>

164
00:08:59,800 --> 00:09:01,780
<i> What a relief!</i>

165
00:09:01,780 --> 00:09:03,180
<i> What do you mean?</i>

166
00:09:04,460 --> 00:09:06,060
<i> I am going to tell Hyeji how I feel about her today.</i>
